Basic Commands List
-------------------

git status		â€“ Show current status of git repository you work in

git init		- Initialize a git repository in the current folder

git add	Filename 	- Add or update "Filename" for the next commit
git add .		- Add or update all files in current folder for the next commit
git add -A		- Add or update all files in current folder (recursive) for next commit

git commit -m "Message"	- Commit added files to git repository
